responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "DCFCB5DD476D5ACDA90284B969934A8A", "The Divine Carnage are the mortal cult of Hecatomb, harbinger of hexes and disciples of Duzahk. They have been on my heels for months. No doubt they can kill two birds with one stone here, if not stopped. No doubt, you have met one of me before we both meet our demise.")
